Boluwatife Akin-Olugbade  Boluwatife Akin-Olugbade Nigerian billionaire businessman Boluwatife Akin-Olugbade is reportedly dead. According to reports, the businessman passed on today January 13th after battling with COVID-19 complications. He was put on oxygen for some days until his demise today. Boluwatife Olugbade is well known for his collection of Rolls Royce with customized number plates; Bolu1, 2, 3,4 5…..”. He died aged 64.